<p class="">I will reply to the first part of my hon. Friend's supplementary question, which I think is the only relevant part. It is true that we would not seek to instruct the Australian representative, who represents the Dominions as well as ourselves, but we have a Commission in Washington on which we are represented.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
